934
00:43:04,150 --> 00:43:06,190
I no longer have a brother.

935
00:43:08,320 --> 00:43:10,030
I truly regret it.

936
00:43:10,960 --> 00:43:11,920
Regret what?

937
00:43:12,320 --> 00:43:14,620
Regret putting you on the throne.

